<P>Lord Dunmore, having thus abandoned his govern|ment, attempted to reduce by force tho&s;e whom he co<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> no longer govern. Some of the mo&s;t &s;trenuous <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">|herents to the Briti&s;h cau&s;e, whom their zeal had r<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">|dered obnoxious at home, now repaired to him. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> was al&s;o joined by numbers of black &s;laves. With the<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">
